            <div type="transcript" id="F508A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Pit - but Heaven over<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 it -</l>
                    <l>And Heaven beside, and<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Heaven abroad; </l>
                    <l>And yet a Pit - </l>
                    <l>With Heaven over it.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To stir would be to slip -</l>
                    <l>To look would be to drop - </l>
                    <l>To dream - to sap the Prop </l>
                    <l>That holds my chances up.  </l>
                    <l>Ah! Pit! With Heaven<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 over it!<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The depth is all my<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thought -</l>
                    <l>I dare not ask my<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 feet - </l>
                    <l>'Twould start us where<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 we sit </l>
                    <l>So straight you'd scarce<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 suspect </l>
                    <l>It was a Pit - with<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 fathoms under it </l>
                    <l><app type="emendation"><lem>Its</lem><rdg>It&#x27;s</rdg></app>
 Circuit just the same</l>
                    <l>Whose Doom to whom </l>
                    <l>'Twould start them - </l>
                    <l>We - could tremble - </l>
                    <l>But since we got a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Bomb - </l>
                    <l>And held it in our Bosom -</l>
                    <l>Nay - Hold it - it is calm - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
